{"timestamp": "2026-07-18 18:03:21,174", "level": "INFO", "logger": "flow.execution", "module": "logging_config", "function": "log_execution_result", "line": 199, "message": "{\"timestamp\": \"2026-07-18T18:03:21.174394\", \"task_id\": \"task0\", \"agent_id\": \"4\", \"objective\": \"Analyze the job description\", \"result\": \"### Job Description Analysis Structure\\n\\nThis section outlines the key components extracted and analyzed from a job description to inform subsequent hiring steps.\\n\\n**1. Role Identification & Context:**\\n*   **Job Title:** The official designation of the position.\\n*   **Department/Team:** The organizational unit the role belongs to.\\n*   **Reporting Structure:** The immediate supervisor and, if specified, direct reports.\\n*   **Role Purpose/Mission:** A concise statement defining the core objective and value proposition of the role within the organization.\\n\\n**2. Key Responsibilities & Duties:**\\n*   **Primary Accountabilities:** Core daily, weekly, or monthly tasks essential to the role.\\n*   **Project Involvement:** Responsibilities related to leading, contributing to, or managing specific projects.\\n*   **Collaboration & Communication:** Expectations for interaction with internal teams, external stakeholders, or clients.\\n*   **Strategic Contribution:** Duties involving planning, decision-mak...\", \"status\": \"completed\", \"duration_seconds\": 0.0}"}
