{"timestamp": "2026-07-18 18:03:38,329", "level": "INFO", "logger": "flow.execution", "module": "logging_config", "function": "log_execution_result", "line": 199, "message": "{\"timestamp\": \"2026-07-18T18:03:38.329169\", \"task_id\": \"task3\", \"agent_id\": \"6\", \"objective\": \"Send emails as and when needed\", \"result\": \"1.  **Interview Invitation and Scheduling:**\\n    *   **When:** After successful resume screening, to invite a candidate for the first interview round.\\n    *   **Content:** Interview stage, purpose, format (e.g., technical, behavioral), duration, proposed time slots or scheduling link, platform details (e.g., video conference link), and contact for inquiries.\\n\\n2.  **Interview Confirmation and Reminder:**\\n    *   **When:** Immediately after an interview is scheduled, and a reminder 24-48 hours prior to the interview.\\n    *   **Content:** Confirmation of date, time, platform link, interviewer(s) names, and any specific preparation instructions (e.g., coding environment setup).\\n\\n3.  **Post-Interview Acknowledgment:**\\n    *   **When:** Within 24 hours of an interview's completion.\\n    *   **Content:** Express thanks for the candidate's time, acknowledge completion of the interview, and provide an estimated timeline for next steps or feedback.\\n\\n4.  **Logistical Update or Rescheduling:**\\n    ...\", \"status\": \"completed\", \"duration_seconds\": 0.0}"}
